description:
By request, a random selection of &quot;Another UFO&quot; episodes of Negativland's Over the Edge radio show on KPFA. ( &lt;a href=&quot; http://www.negativland.com/ote/?page_id=36&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt; http://www.negativland.com/ote/?page_id=36&lt;/a&gt; ) For those unfamiliar with OTE, this is a good sampler pack spanning over a decade of the show and, to my mind, great background music for Halloween. OTE, at its best, can manage a certain level of creepiness, induce a sense that the world is not as we know it to be, and &quot;Another UFO&quot; manages to live within that space more than any other series on OTE. Unlike the torrents of the most recent episodes from 2012 on, these are as I found them with no edits to the ID3 tags and I will admit that I haven't actually listened to them. Buyer beware.
As always, to support this work, contribute to Negativland here: &lt;a href=&quot; http://www.negativland.com/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt; http://www.negativland.com/&lt;/a&gt;
and KPFA here: &lt;a href=&quot; http://www.kpfa.org/&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt; http://www.kpfa.org/&lt;/a&gt;
If you have OTE episodes to share, please comment or add a torrent of your own. And remember, don't say &quot;Hello.&quot;
